data.description: Seller has been transferred for work! Seller's loss is YOUR GAIN! GORGEOUS, barely lived in new construction home on a large level lot. Luxury vinyl plank  throughout the main living areas, formal dining room with wainscotting, a convenient half bath and wonderful, large open concept family  living area will make this your dream home. Featuring a large island with seating, granite and stainless appliances including a gas range,  you will enjoy spending time in the kitchen while overlooking the fireside family room. Easy access to the COVERED back patio makes  Summer BBQing a breeze! Upstairs you'll find the large Primary bedroom with a spa-like ensuite boasting a soaking tub and shower as well  as a great walk-in closet. The additional 3 bedrooms upstairs share a great secondary bathroom. 3 car garage for the golf cart,  DOWNTOWN Jefferson location and walking distance to all area amenities. NO HOA either! This is your dream home!
